	dprr:hasNoteText "Quaestor Syria 50 (MR 2.250). Read (L.) Marius. The praenomen depends on identification with RE no. 20. See Ascon. 19C, where an accuser of Scaurus in 54 is named L. Marius L. f. (TJC)\n" ;
